867cde852d980da359e5f6f35c27dc96b513d65a345bb11cb9" style=3D"color:#d40000;=
text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">took a look at Mass
MoCA</a></u>, whose newish director recently released a strategic plan for =
the next 16 years of the museum=E2=80=99s trajectory. Founded by a group fr=
om nearby Williams College Museum of Art, the museum was first conceived in=
 the late 1980s after North Adams=E2=80=99s largest employer, the Sprague E=
lectric Company, closed its plant in the town, removing an economic engine =
from the community that once employed 4,000 persons, or 20 percent of the p=
opulation. <br/><br/>The <i>Globe</i>, assessing the impact of the museum o=
